266
00:23:08,706 --> 00:23:14,530
Those years were filled with learning, and the greatest lesson was that there is no substitution for hard work.

267
00:23:15,530 --> 00:23:19,512
At Suffolk, I received a Bachelor of Science in Business with a major in Accounting.

268
00:23:20,373 --> 00:23:23,575
