288
00:25:02,463 --> 00:25:05,244
We want a Medford that can be the greatest it can be.

289
00:25:06,085 --> 00:25:09,286
So when I say to you that I will be accountable, it's not a slogan.

290
00:25:10,226 --> 00:25:13,928
It is my acknowledgment that the work of government is never done alone.

291
00:25:13,948 --> 00:25:16,429
It is never the work of one person.

292
00:25:17,189 --> 00:25:23,632
We live in a democracy and we work in collaboration with each other, and that is why I call each of you a partner in progress.

293
00:25:25,726 --> 00:25:28,007
As I stated, I'm a certified public accountant.

294
00:25:28,167 --> 00:25:32,950
My professional experience has brought me a deep understanding of the value of managing assets.

295
00:25:33,490 --> 00:25:34,751
It is second nature to me.

296
00:25:35,331 --> 00:25:45,237
And simply put, a well-managed city is one where the resources and assets of the city are identified, needs are assessed, and needs are fulfilled.

297
00:25:46,118 --> 00:25:48,279
As we all know, this requires funding.

298
00:25:50,245 --> 00:25:56,327
My administration has and will continue to be a responsible steward of our taxpayers' hard-earned dollars.

299
00:25:56,947 --> 00:26:00,948
We will continue to aggressively pursue grant funding to leverage our dollars.

300
00:26:01,988 --> 00:26:04,489
Medford's high quality bond rating is no accident.

301
00:26:04,929 --> 00:26:10,911
It's the result of careful planning and a prudent expenditure of municipal funds to projects that better our city.

302
00:26:11,671 --> 00:26:16,112
Just today, we were listed as a top 10 list of most successful cities by Zipia.

303
00:26:16,973 --> 00:26:17,853
We're quite proud of that.

304
00:26:18,793 --> 00:26:28,975
My administration has also been accountable where the rubber meets the road, literally through the Complete Streets Initiative, which we brought into the city of Medford within three months of me being sworn into office.

305
00:26:29,875 --> 00:26:37,617
We have moved forward to repave and fix major roads throughout every section of the city, which will make it safer for pedestrians, bicyclists, and vehicles.

306
00:26:38,417 --> 00:26:42,598
Our infrastructure needs are continually being addressed through the efforts of our Department of Public Works.

307
00:26:44,448 --> 00:26:48,850
I am proud of tackling the issues of the need of a new police station head-on.

308
00:26:49,611 --> 00:26:53,232
For years, the rundown condition of the police department headquarters has been known.

309
00:26:53,933 --> 00:26:56,874
For years, this one condition was not adequately addressed.

310
00:26:57,515 --> 00:27:01,337
But I did not choose to look in the rearview mirror and ask why.

311
00:27:01,857 --> 00:27:03,458
Rather, I have chosen to look forward.

312
00:27:04,158 --> 00:27:08,160
Because the starting point of all success is action, not blame.

313
00:27:08,901 --> 00:27:12,983
So my administration initiated the process to build a new state-of-the-art police station.

314
00:27:13,363 --> 00:27:15,884
We've been meeting weekly now for over three months.

315
00:27:16,424 --> 00:27:24,649
It's a team that's comprised of our police chief, our city engineer, our environmentalist, as well as members of the police squad from all levels.

316
00:27:25,129 --> 00:27:32,037
men, female, that have been visiting police stations around our state and around our area to find out what's the best and what's the worst.

317
00:27:32,157 --> 00:27:32,777
What do we like?

318
00:27:32,817 --> 00:27:41,987
What do we want our station to have so that we do it right once, not have to go back and make changes two years down the road because it's the police headquarters that simply doesn't work.

319
00:27:43,098 --> 00:27:50,764
Our fine law enforcement personnel deserve nothing less, as they serve the safety needs of our residents every hour of every day of every night.

320
00:27:51,765 --> 00:27:54,567
In the world in which we live, safety can never be taken for granted.

321
00:27:54,588 --> 00:27:59,832
The needs of our public safety employees are many, and they must continually be addressed.

322
00:28:01,192 --> 00:28:02,152
We have done just that.

323
00:28:02,172 --> 00:28:14,297
In year one of our five-year capital plan, the city has purchased 12 new police cruisers, breathing apparatus and turnout gear for our firefighters, new trucks and equipment for our DPW employees.

324
00:28:15,818 --> 00:28:19,319
However, public safety and public health is more than new equipment.

325
00:28:19,820 --> 00:28:25,442
It is the converging of all departments and levels of government to come together to fight an epidemic.

326
00:28:26,410 --> 00:28:28,632
Of course, I'm speaking of the opioid crisis.

327
00:28:29,332 --> 00:28:36,097
Every Medford family stands shoulder to shoulder with each other in the fight against this reality.

328
00:28:36,917 --> 00:28:39,679
When one of our families suffers, we all suffer.

329
00:28:40,600 --> 00:28:47,405
