330
00:28:48,125 --> 00:28:54,751
For the first time, there's someone who has a specific purpose to work within our community, along with various agencies.

331
00:28:55,271 --> 00:29:11,866
Marion Ryan, our district attorney, has monthly forums up at the Lawrence Memorial Hospital, where she brings together public health officials, City of Medford employees, police, fire from a multitude of communities to talk about this issue and to determine best practices.

332
00:29:12,127 --> 00:29:13,508
This is already being done today.

333
00:29:17,330 --> 00:29:21,371
This is a disease that is so decimating to so many, especially our young people.

334
00:29:23,412 --> 00:29:29,954
