345
00:30:22,323 --> 00:30:31,987
This is an effort to transform a portion of Medford Square into a multi-use space to allow residents to engage in passive recreation or simply enjoy a community event.

346
00:30:32,567 --> 00:30:35,548
Sense of community and quality of life go hand in hand.

347
00:30:35,928 --> 00:30:38,489
We need these community spaces in order to do that.

348
00:30:40,070 --> 00:30:43,911
Investment in a city also means to put its resources to their optimal use.

349
00:30:44,512 --> 00:30:47,553
